{"tid":180493,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"買左個冒牌手袋報海關其實揾唔揾得到條友?","createTime":"2017-03-31T03:14:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-31T05:17:50.000Z","uid":992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d9ad968f076d42f7d5da303521d22afc9914e920","tid":180493,"uid":992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T03:14:55.000Z","msg":"是源係Carousell個拍賣到幫朋友買左個YSL手袋$5000,<br />\n後尾個朋友唔太鐘意個袋,想放返出去,先發現原來個袋係假野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後揾返個條友幾次都比佢block<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n知道個賣家條仔車牌號碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 應該係情侣黎一齊昆人<br />\n有冇咩方法可以揾到條友追返啲錢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淨係知車牌係TL4476<br />\n同埋住葵興<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1cajW0e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1cajW0e.jpg&h=3c20ba6d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/31/111229_812f07762074ba3eedb96578f42084c3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F31%2F111229_812f07762074ba3eedb96578f42084c3.jpg&h=6c72938e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/31/111229_2813641a109aadebc564b1aed30eac3c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F31%2F111229_2813641a109aadebc564b1aed30eac3c.jpg&h=ce9d4422&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wOEStBj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwOEStBj.jpg&h=47902016&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b13f7639320e6fea93771662be00f3f89c11bea1","tid":180493,"uid":97409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T03:16:28.000Z","msg":"報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e826e1f7b